Lafarge Cement Zimbabwe’s Annual Profit Unchanged as Credit Isn’t Repeated

-- B y   N e l s o n   G o r e   B a n y a
-- 
2011-03-17T07:36:56Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-17/lafarge-cement-zimbabwe-s-annual-profit-unchanged-as-credit-isn-t-repeated.html
  Lafarge Cement Zimbabwe Ltd. (LAFARGE)  said
net income for the 12 months through December was unchanged at
$2.7 million as a tax credit wasn’t repeated.  Revenue for the period increased to $41.7 million from
$28.3 million a year earlier, the company said in an
advetisement published in the Harare-based Herald newspaper
today. The company paid taxes of $1.05 million, compared with a
credit of $1.15 million in 2009, it said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Nelson Gore Banya in Johannesburg at 
 ngbanya@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alastair Reed at 
 areed12@bloomberg.net  